1 - Register in each forum.
2 - Add a sponsored link on your signature.
3 - Get visible threads using google alerts.
-----------------------------------------------------
1 - List of Car Forums available online
https://zone1b.com/threads/list-of-car-forums-available-online.2325/

2 - Promote car related products.

Example on how to locate signature field
https://www.hyundai-forums.com/account/signature

3 - Go to Google Alerts (https://www.google.com/alerts) and create alerts for the forums.
Use it to receive email notifications when any new content from the forums become visible
and try to reply as much as you can.
